  "market_context": "USOIL was in an uptrend, having rallied from a swing low near 79.58 to a swing high near 89.67. Price then retraced downward and found support within the Fibonacci golden zone (0.5–0.618 levels), triggering a bullish reversal.",
  "key_observation": "Price retraced into the customized golden zone (0.5 at 84.63 and 0.618 at 85.43/85.82), formed a reversal candle, and moved higher—validating the golden zone as a high-probability reversal area.",
  "analysis_steps": [
    "Step 1: The analyst configured the Fibonacci Retracement tool to display only 0, 0.5, and 0.618 levels, coloring 0.5 gray and 0.618 yellow to highlight the 'golden zone'.",
    "Step 2: The analyst drew the Fibonacci tool from a swing low (79.58) to a swing high (89.67) on the USOIL daily chart.",
    "Step 3: The analyst observed that price retraced down and paused within the golden zone (between 84.63 and 85.82), where it reversed upward with bullish momentum candles.",
    "Step 4: The analyst emphasized that this reversal confirmed the utility of the golden zone for identifying high-probability entry zones in trending markets."
  ],
  "outcome": null,
  "lessons": "Customizing Fibonacci to focus on the 0.5–0.618 zone improves visual clarity; price often reverses in this 'golden zone' after a strong impulsive move, especially when aligned with trend structure.",
